Following the tragedy which claimed over 60 lives in the Russian city of Kemerovo, president Danny Faure has expressed the condolences of the Government and people of the Republic of Seychelles to H.E. Mr. Vladimir Putin, President of the Russian Federation.  “In this period of grief, I wish strength and fortitude to the victims families in the face of this terrible tragedy. The people of Seychelles join me in praying for the souls of those that perished,” said President Faure. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Republic of Seychelles.